history.content:
Dear students, 

We are hoping to expand 127/227A so that all students who are interested can get in, so do sign up and add yourself to the waitlist if you are interested. We are going to do our best to expand the class, though we cannot promise this yet.

EDIT: The class has now expanded to 400 students.
